HEADWORD: Afterpiece
<hw>Aft"er*piece`</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧f"t⟦etil⟧r*p⟦emac⟧s`)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A piece performed after a play, usually a
